== Honors ==
In 2010, to honor Joseph's exploits in the sport of boxing, the town of Sogakope in the Volta Region of Ghana enstooled him as a warrior chief. His enstoolment name was Togbe Kaletor I, which means 'Brave Warrior.'<ref> [http://news.myjoyonline.com/sports/201012/58350.asp "Agbeko enstooled Warrior Chief in Volta Region"], My Joy Online(Ghana), December 28, 2010</ref>

